reviewText:
The wife is eighteen, which is old enough to get married but not old enough to drink.
She has a nice tush.  The husband is a bit older.  They have to attend a party.  The
wife is not ready, so the husband spends the entire movie spanking her with one
instrument or another.  You get to wondering where all these toys come from.
This movie will not get any awards for acting ability, direction, writing, or anything else,
but the movie makes a nice diversion.
